text: Bayasgalangiin Solongo is a basketball player from Mongolia. Solongo competed at the 2020 Summer Olympics.Solongo BAYASGALAN She was born on 6 February 1990.Bayasgalan Solongo == References == Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Mongolian basketball players Category:Olympians for Mongolia Category:People from Ulaanbaatar
